Responsibilities
Write to customers in their terms and on their level so that the advertiser's sales message is more readily received.Discuss with Project Manager regarding client product, advertising themes and methods, and any changes that should be made in advertising copy.Write advertising copy for use by publication, broadcast or internet media to promote the sale of goods and services.Present drafts and ideas to Project Manager..Vary language and tone of messages based on product and medium.Consult with Product Manager, Sales, Media and Marketing Representatives to obtain information on product or service and discuss style and length of advertising copy.Edit or rewrite existing copy as necessary, and submit copy for approval by Project Manager. Requirements : Diploma Degree/Bachelor Degree from any major, Preferably in Communication, Marketing or English Literature.At least 2 years of working experiences as translators/transcreation (are preferably)Excellent in English, both written and spokenAble to think out of the box, creative thinker, and innovative.Having knowledge in marketing/automotive/medical/chemical/IT/Legal is an advantageGood time management skillAble to take initiative, and working independently, a self-motivated person, have an eye on details, able to work under pressure with tight deadlines, integrity and leadership Please send your latest CV and Photograph to :recruitment@star-indonesia.co.idWrite “Transcreation ENG-INDO” as your subject email
